                    {
                      "id": "1b6c58f",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p>At the heart of our foundation's mission is <strong>Vetiver Grass Technology (VGT)</strong>, an eco-friendly system that uses vetiver grass (Vetiveria zizanioides) for a wide range of applications, such as soil and water conservation, slope stabilization, disaster mitigation, land rehabilitation, and pollution control. This innovative solution, known as the <strong>Vetiver System (VS)</strong>, is recognized for its deep-rooted effectiveness in preventing soil erosion and protecting infrastructure from natural disasters like landslides and floods.</p>",
