            {
              "id": "0c2fcb8",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Not only does Vetiver Grass provide unparalleled environmental benefits, but it also supports sustainable livelihoods for communities. By planting and maintaining Vetiver systems, local communities can benefit from its by-products, such as its use in handicrafts, animal feed, and even essential oil production. In countries like India and Vietnam, Vetiver has played a key role in both restoring land and improving the economic resilience of rural populations.</p>",
                "align": "center",
                "text_color": "#FFFFFF",
